        "releaseNotesTooltip": "<div><span class=\"tooltip-title\">What's new in DOCA 2.2.0:</span><ul><li>Enhancements to BlueField NIC mode </li><li>DOCA PCC (Beta) for Programmable Congestion Control</li><li>Data-Path-Accelerator (DPA) DOCA FlexIO (GA)</li><li>DOCA FLOW enhancements for VPC overlay acceleration (Geneve and GRE)</li><li>DOCA FLOW per-flow metering</li><li>OVS-DOCA (Beta)</li><li>DOCA profiles (package install options) \u2013 Introducing DOCA-OFED profile</li><li>BMC/Redfish enhancements</li><li>Allowing DOCA-Services installation on devices with no internet access</li><li>Additional Host and DPU OSs are now supported</li></ul><a href=\"https://docs.nvidia.com/doca/sdk/release-notes/index.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"tooltip-link\">Open Release Notes</a></div>",
